    "inheritedQuestion": "The Sophistic challenge: Is virtue teachable? Is truth relative or objective?",
    "bequeathedQuestion": [
      "What is the nature of the good life?",
      "Can ethical knowledge be taught?",
      "What is the relationship between the soul and moral action?"
